MasterChef South Africa - Season 3, Episode 1




MasterChef South Africa returned to South Africa's TV screens with a bang as M-Net's massively popular culinary showdown debuted its third Season with some impressive twists right in the opening few minutes: a brand new celebrity Judge, in the tall, dark and handsome form of the Spice King himself, Reuben Riffel, as well as a new Boot Camp backdrop: the picturesque Cape Town harbour!




Original Air Date: 21-Aug-2014
